# BookNest - Online Bookstore Management System

BookNest is a Java-based online bookstore management system built using JSP, Servlets, JDBC, MySQL, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript.

The project is designed with multiple user roles including Admin, Seller, and Customer. It currently includes database setup, MVC structure, authentication pages, admin dashboard, seller dashboard, seller book management, and basic dashboard UI screens.

